    "This figure indicates a relatively healthy job market, as unemployment rates around 4 percent are generally considered low and typical of a stable economy.",
    "From Linear Scripts to Complex LangGraph AgentsWhile our economic data retrieval agent demonstrates the core concepts of AI agents effectively, it represents what we might call a \"first-generation\" approach to agent design.",
